Business Brief -- Caterpillar Inc.:
   Unit and Mitsubishi Heavy
   Agree to a Joint Venture
The new venture, Mitsubishi Caterpillar Forklift, will
make lift trucks and other material-handling equipment.
Mitsubishi will own 80% of the equity of the new company and
Caterpillar will own 20%.
   Caterpillar said the value of assets transferred to the
venture by it and Mitsubishi will be determined on or about
July 1, the date the venture takes effect.
   The venture must be approved by the U.S., Japanese and
European Community authorities.